for adapting to this plane.

00:08:37.190 --> 00:08:38.570 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:08:38.570 --> 00:08:39.890 align:middle line:90%
>> I mean, I am--

00:08:39.890 --> 00:08:42.880 align:middle line:90%


00:08:42.880 --> 00:08:46.490 align:middle line:84%
I'm a consciousness,
