00:08:46.490 --> 00:08:48.620 align:middle line:90%
localized in the brain.

00:08:48.620 --> 00:09:01.600 align:middle line:10%
And consciousness is heart and
not material manifestation.

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:04.340 align:middle line:10%
>> Hmm.

00:09:04.340 --> 00:09:10.220 align:middle line:10%
>> They-- the doctors,
they treated me--

00:09:10.220 --> 00:09:12.860 align:middle line:10%
they treated that as--

00:09:12.860 --> 00:09:17.120 align:middle line:10%
that as psychosis.

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:18.080 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes.

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:19.280 align:middle line:10%
That's unfortunate.

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:21.680 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:09:21.680 --> 00:09:25.110 align:middle line:84%
I said that they was
the psychotic ones,

00:09:25.110 --> 00:09:28.430 align:middle line:90%
but you understand that--

00:09:28.430 --> 00:09:30.710 align:middle line:90%
>> I understand perfectly well.

00:09:30.710 --> 00:09:35.740 align:middle line:84%
Mainstream Western reality
is metaphysically ignorant.

00:09:35.740 --> 00:09:37.070 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, that's right.

00:09:37.070 --> 00:09:42.930 align:middle line:84%
Because they're
philosophical materialists.

00:09:42.930 --> 00:09:43.730 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:09:43.730 --> 00:09:49.100 align:middle line:84%
But I have no question that
being with you now, I'm

00:09:49.100 --> 00:09:51.890 align:middle line:84%
in the presence
of a soul of being

00:09:51.890 --> 00:09:53.660 align:middle line:90%
