00:09:53.660 --> 00:09:55.073 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, yes.

00:09:55.073 --> 00:09:57.365 align:middle line:84%
>> And I know that's an
important part of your message.

00:09:57.365 --> 00:09:59.945 align:middle line:90%


00:09:59.945 --> 00:10:01.310 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:10:01.310 --> 00:10:02.460 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:10:02.460 --> 00:10:09.376 align:middle line:84%
And you can see it
because you are it.

00:10:09.376 --> 00:10:10.800 align:middle line:90%
I mean, just like--

00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:13.800 align:middle line:90%


