00:10:24.820 --> 00:10:25.620 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:10:25.620 --> 00:10:26.470 align:middle line:90%
It's a resonance.

00:10:26.470 --> 00:10:31.740 align:middle line:84%
I feel like a bubbliness, an
incredible fizzy feeling just

00:10:31.740 --> 00:10:33.805 align:middle line:90%
