00:10:33.805 --> 00:10:34.720 align:middle line:90%
>> A fizzy feeling?

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:35.790 align:middle line:90%
>> A fizzy feeling.

00:10:35.790 --> 00:10:36.608 align:middle line:90%
Really

00:10:36.608 --> 00:10:39.730 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:10:39.730 --> 00:10:40.530 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:10:40.530 --> 00:10:42.830 align:middle line:84%
